'''Lansana Mansaray''' (wavutse 1992), bakunze kwita '''Barmmy Boy''', ni umukinnyi wa firime wo [[Siyera Lewone|muri Siyera Lewone]] .   Umwe mu bakora amafilime azwi cyane muri sinema ya [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone, Mansaray azwi cyane muri filime zizwi cyane ''Youth'', ''Charity'' and [[:en:Survivors_(2018_film)|''Survivors'']]. . Usibye gukora firime, anatunganya firime, umukinnyi wa cinemateri numuraperi.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1992 i Freetown, muri [[Siyera Lewone|Siyera]] Lewone. 

== Umwuga ==
Mansaray ni we washinze WeOwnTV akaba n'umuyobozi ushinzwe umusaruro muri Freetown Media Center. Hamwe na WeOwnTV, yakoranye n’imiryango myinshi irimo: Defence for Children International, Studios ya NOVA (UK), Inama y’Ubwongereza Siyera Lewone, UNICEF Sierra Leone, Save the Children Sierra Leone, Ivuriro ry’umugore n’umugi wa Hull UK 2017 . 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, yayoboye filime ye ya mbere ''Youth'' . Muri uwo mwaka, yakoze nk'umukinnyi wa sinema muri filime ''y'abagiraneza'' . Yakomeje gukora nka cinematif mu myaka iri imbere muri firime; ''Barwanyije'' (2011) kandi ''Ubumuga ni Ubushobozi'' . 

Usibye bo, yakoze nk'umukinnyi wa sinema mu bikorwa byinshi byegukanye ibihembo ''nka'' ''Decisions'' in 2011, ''Girl Rising'' in 2013, ''They Are We'' in 2014, and ''Meet the Africans: Many Rivers to Cross'' in 2013, aho  nyuma yatsinze  Igihembo cya Emmy .  Mu mwaka wa 2014, yasuye u [[Bwongereza]] kugira ngo abonane n'incuti zimwe na zimwe, ariko byabaye ngombwa ko yongerera igihe cy'amezi atanu kubera icyorezo cya Ebola muri Siyera Lewone . 

Muri 2018, yayoboye filime documentaire ''Survivors'', ishingiye ku kibazo cya Ebola. Nyuma yaje gutorwa muri Emmy's Best Social Issue Documentary, aho ibaye filime ya mbere yo muri [[Afurika|Afrika]] yuburengerazuba yakiriye ishimwe. 

